00:39:37.800 --> 00:39:40.170
And there's actually a
very helpful community

00:39:40.170 --> 00:39:44.750
around there trying to
get a sense for why is it

00:39:44.750 --> 00:39:49.350
that it's only 16% of op
eds are written by women?

00:39:49.350 --> 00:39:52.540
And is this a place where
you could sort of put a lever

00:39:52.540 --> 00:39:54.500
and try to get not
only gender diversity

00:39:54.500 --> 00:39:57.754
but cognitive diversity
